const modalList = [
  {
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/typr.jpg"),
    modalvideo: require("../../videos/Typr.mov"),
    modalTitle: "Speed Typr",
    modalDescription: `Speed Typr is a game I made with React Javascript and node
                express server. Where random words fall down from the screen and
                you type as many words as you can before the time runs out.`
  },
  {
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/stock.jpg"),
    modalvideo: require("../../videos/instock.mov"),
    modalTitle: "InStock",
    modalDescription: `InStock is a warehouse site made with my BrainStation classmates
                Ana Provirina, Lukas Richardson, and Tyler Noseworthy. This
                project was incredibly valuable. We used a Jira board, which
                taught me so much about dividing tasks among the group and
                communicating what needs to be done. Also learned about merging
                and dealing with conflicts with other people's code.`
  },
  {
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/brain.jpg"),
    modalvideo: require("../../videos/brain.mov"),
    modalTitle: "Brainflix",
    modalDescription: `BrainFlix is a YouTube clone that I made with React JavaScript 
      and node express server. 
      Also with a working comment section that you can comment on videos you like.`
  },
  {
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/band.jpg"),
    modalvideo: require("../../videos/band.mov"),
    modalTitle: "Bee's Knees BandPage",
    modalDescription: `The Bee's knees band page that I made with Html5 and CSS. 
      Also with a working comment section where you add your name and comment about the band.`
  },
  {
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/duenas.png"),
    buttonImage: require("../../Images/duenas.png"),
    modalTitle: "Duenas Services",
    modalDescription: `Project I'm working on at the moment is making a new website with React.js for
    Duenas Services company.`
  }
];

export default modalList;
